); }; const styles = { container: { textAlign: 'center', padding: '30px', background: 'linear-gradient(135deg, #f7d9e3, #fcc2e4)', borderRadius: '10px', boxShadow: '0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)', maxWidth: '400px', margin: 'auto', }, heading: { color: '#ff77aa', fontFamily: "'Poppins', sans-serif", marginBottom: '20px', fontSize: '2rem', }, pizza: { width: '250px', height: '250px', position: 'relative', borderRadius: '50%', backgroundColor: '#f1c27d', // Base for the pizza crust boxShadow: 'inset 0px 0px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)', margin: '0 auto', }, crust: { width: '100%', height: '100%', borderRadius: '50%', backgroundColor: '#d28c5a', // Pizza crust boxShadow: '0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)', position: 'absolute', top: 0, left: 0, }, sauce: { width: '90%', height: '90%', borderRadius: '50%', backgroundColor: '#ff6347', // Tomato sauce position: 'absolute', top: '5%', left: '5%', }, cheese: { width: '85%', height: '85%', borderRadius: '50%', backgroundColor: '#f2d34a', // Cheese position: 'absolute', top: '7.5%', left: '7.5%', }, pepperoni1: { width: '20px', height: '20px', backgroundColor: '#ff4d4d', // Pepperoni borderRadius: '50%', position: 'absolute', top: '30%', left: '50%', transform: 'translateX(-50%)', }, pepperoni2: { width: '20px', height: '20px', backgroundColor: '#ff4d4d', borderRadius: '50%', position: 'absolute', top: '50%', left: '40%', }, pepperoni3: { width: '20px', height: '20px', backgroundColor: '#ff4d4d', borderRadius: '50%', position: 'absolute', top: '40%', left: '60%', }, greenPeppers: { width: '15px', height: '15px', backgroundColor: '#9ACD32', // Green peppers borderRadius: '50%', position: 'absolute', top: '20%', left: '30%', }, olives: { width: '12px', height: '12px', backgroundColor: '#2F4F4F', // Black olives borderRadius: '50%', position: 'absolute', top: '40%', left: '70%', }, }; export default RealisticPizza;
